● Bachelor’s degree in accounting or related field, or minimum 5 years experience in full charge bookkeeping, accounting or bookkeeping certification;

● Advanced knowledge of accounting and bookkeeping software, Quickbooks preferred;

● Knowledge of U.S. GAAP or other industry-standard accounting frameworks;

● Expertise in Microsoft Excel or any other spreadsheet;

